rComments: He was really helpful when it came to exams - always go to the review sessions before a test!

I can honestly say Prof. Helle is the best professor I've had thus far. The course has content that could be taught in a boring way and could be very hard to understand, but Prof. Helle teaches it in a very fun and effective way. He is unbelievably knowledgeable about First Amendment law and is a very funny guy. It is a requirement for JOUR majors.
